WEBVTT

00:01.935 --> 00:04.770
(funky disco plays)
♪ My name is Cleveland Brown

00:04.772 --> 00:07.006
♪ And I am proud to be

00:07.008 --> 00:09.108
♪ Right back in my hometown

00:09.110 --> 00:12.111
♪ With my new family

00:12.113 --> 00:14.013
♪ There's old friends
and new friends ♪

00:14.015 --> 00:16.315
♪ And even a bear

00:16.317 --> 00:18.817
♪ Through good times
and bad times ♪

00:18.819 --> 00:20.185
♪ It's true love we share

00:20.187 --> 00:22.521
♪ And so I found a place

00:22.523 --> 00:25.124
♪ Where everyone will know

00:25.126 --> 00:26.959
♪ My happy mustached face

00:26.961 --> 00:28.994
♪ This is <i>The Cleveland Show.</i> ♪

