time for everybody to hide.

00:47.381 --> 00:49.148
Donna, you're the biggest,
so you might want to push

00:49.150 --> 00:51.016
the couch and the
piano together.

00:51.018 --> 00:52.551
Come on, big'un.

00:54.988 --> 00:56.889
Not yet. Not yet.

00:58.858 --> 01:00.392
Not yet. Not yet.

01:01.728 --> 01:04.363
