01:04.365 --> 01:08.400
I call it,
"He Ain't Coming, Mom."

01:11.037 --> 01:13.005
We goin'?

01:13.007 --> 01:16.875
I'm sorry Dad stood you
up on your anniversary.

01:16.877 --> 01:18.377
Please, if I had to be reminded

01:18.379 --> 01:20.846
that I married her
b'tugly-ass every year,

01:20.848 --> 01:22.347
I'd stand her up, too.

01:22.349 --> 01:24.183
Let's go.

01:24.185 --> 01:25.517
WOMAN:
Bye, Lavar.

01:25.519 --> 01:27.419
(vehicle driving away)
Bye, Diane Lane.

01:29.022 --> 01:31.557
Uh, I renamed my car Diane Lane.

01:31.559 --> 01:34.026
Ooh, I'm naming
mine Carol.

01:34.028 --> 01:35.027
Happy Anniv....

01:35.029 --> 01:38.030
Ow! My breathing nose.

01:38.032 --> 01:39.565
What are you all doing
in my house?

01:39.567 --> 01:41.600
