anniversary party, Lavar,

01:41.602 --> 01:44.570
and you were supposed
to be here hours ago.

01:44.572 --> 01:46.738
(sobbing)
Now you know how I felt

01:46.740 --> 01:49.074
when you were late
and we got stuck with Cleveland.

01:49.076 --> 01:50.542
That's me!

01:50.544 --> 01:51.877
Wait.

01:51.879 --> 01:54.179
(sobbing)

01:56.416 --> 01:58.117
Aw, this ain't Toys"R"Us.

01:58.119 --> 01:59.218
You're a liar, Mama.

01:59.220 --> 02:00.419
