02:00.421 --> 02:02.888
Gotta grab me a big thing
of pretzels.

02:02.890 --> 02:05.224
A minute?
That never means a minute.

02:05.226 --> 02:07.059
What are we gonna do?

02:07.061 --> 02:10.062
This place is so <i>booooring.</i>

02:10.064 --> 02:12.464
What?
This place is amazing.

02:12.466 --> 02:14.066
What are you
doing, man?

02:14.068 --> 02:16.468
