02:33.254 --> 02:36.588
and then go stare at
some screen savers.

02:36.590 --> 02:39.491
I'm sorry, Junior,
but this unit has been sold.

02:39.493 --> 02:41.593
What? But I've been
playing office here

02:41.595 --> 02:43.495
for a year and a half.

02:43.497 --> 02:45.964
I know. And nothing has brought
a smile to my face

02:45.966 --> 02:48.267
more than seeing you grow
Cleveland Jr. Industries

02:48.269 --> 02:50.135
from a fake mom-and-pop
organization

02:50.137 --> 02:52.337
to a fake international
conglomerate.

02:52.339 --> 02:55.140
But I'm afraid floor models
don't last forever.

02:55.142 --> 02:57.142
Can you give me a
moment to say good-bye?

02:57.144 --> 02:59.278
Take all the time
you need.

02:59.280 --> 03:01.280
