it's like in a real office.

03:07.288 --> 03:10.622
(sighs)
That's always been my dream.

03:10.624 --> 03:12.624
Someday.

03:12.626 --> 03:15.093
Or maybe today.

03:17.130 --> 03:20.299
(grunting)

03:20.301 --> 03:21.967
