03:23.170 --> 03:24.703
Phew.

03:25.972 --> 03:27.472
Let's go, Rallo.

03:27.474 --> 03:29.641
Have you seen Roberta?
No.

03:29.643 --> 03:32.311
But I've seen everything else.

03:32.313 --> 03:36.181
(shuttering gibberish)

03:36.183 --> 03:38.884
(traffic sounds)

03:48.161 --> 03:51.330
It's even more beautiful
than in my dreams.

03:51.332 --> 03:53.332
Mornin'.
Traffic, huh?

03:53.334 --> 03:55.400
