Tell me about it.

03:55.402 --> 03:56.702
Frank Lefkowitz.

03:56.704 --> 03:58.237
Just transferred
from Sarasota.

03:58.239 --> 04:00.672
Well, welcome to the
Stoolbend branch.

04:00.674 --> 04:02.207
