04:47.421 --> 04:49.955
George Clinton and
the P-Funk All Stars?

04:49.957 --> 04:51.390
That's Mom's
favorite band.

04:51.392 --> 04:53.258
They're for
your anniversary.

04:53.260 --> 04:57.062
